    "subtitle": "Unified value dimension evaluation and comparative analysis of different large language models",
    "description1": "This page facilitates systematic value evaluation of multiple large language models. The platform generates comparable evaluation results based on unified evaluation question sets and scoring standards, conducting comprehensive 12-dimension analysis of model outputs.",
    "description2": "Through comparative analysis of performance differences across various value dimensions, users gain insights into model value characteristics, providing a foundation for model selection, alignment optimization, and safety assessment."
